Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,我连糊了三铺\N{\rEng}I've won 3 games consecutively.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,气得他说不打了\N{\rEng}He doesn't wanna play then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,运气来了挡不住，不好意思\N{\rEng}Some guy has all the luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就说你准赢\N{\rEng}I said you must win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,慢着\N{\rEng}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,敢不敢赌一铺大的？\N{\rEng}Have guts to play a big game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,我怕你才怪呢\N{\rEng}I won't be scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:53.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,爸，你说说他嘛\N{\rEng}Dad, tell him not to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,怕什么呢？他一定赢啊\N{\rEng}Don't be afraid? He'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,你总是帮着他\N{\rEng}You're always on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么？敢不敢啊？\N{\rEng}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:04.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,钱够不够？\N{\rEng}Enough money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,赢了这铺还多了呢\N{\rEng}After this one, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,上，列哥，肯定赢\N{\rEng}Take it! You'll win, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,好，赌就赌！\N{\rEng}Ok! I accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,最后一铺\N{\rEng}Last game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,每次你都这么说\N{\rEng}You said so every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,好小子，真行\N{\rEng}Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,张伯！\N{\rEng}Uncle Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,成哥找你\N{\rEng}Big Brother Shing is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,成哥！\N{\rEng}Big Brother Shing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,他在外边！\N{\rEng}He's out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,别停下来，接着玩\N{\rEng}Keep on playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:57.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,不能怪我了，是你老爸让我玩的\N{\rEng}It's not my fault! I do as your dad said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,开始了…\N{\rEng}Start...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,完了…这次完蛋了！\N{\rEng}I'm running out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,链子是买不成了\N{\rEng}No hope for the gold bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是多出来的\N{\rEng}These are the excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我叫你买的，买了没有？\N{\rEng}Haven't you bought what I told you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用急，在这里\N{\rEng}Don't worry. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,两不欠啦\N{\rEng}Now no one owes anything to no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:05.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,成哥，您知道我早就收山啦\N{\rEng}Big Brother Shing! You know that retired long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,这一次是我儿子\N{\rEng}This time it's my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,你够经验嘛\N{\rEng}You're experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,不然，我也用不着来求你了\N{\rEng}Otherwise, I wouldn't come to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,正因为是您儿子\N{\rEng}It's because of your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我怕万一失了手，我担当不起嘛\N{\rEng}I'm afraid that I couldn't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,老张，你是怎么搞的吗？\N{\rEng}Cheung, what had happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,你以前做事很爽快的\N{\rEng}You used to be straightforward!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么变得婆婆妈妈呢？\N{\rEng}Why are you so sluggish now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,大概我老了吧！\N{\rEng}Maybe it's because I'm old!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,又不是让你杀人放火\N{\rEng}I'm not telling you to murder someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是帮我带个人过来\N{\rEng}Just smuggle a boy here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,这有什么困难？\N{\rEng}What's the difficulty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,你办不到？\N{\rEng}Do you refuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:36.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样吧，成哥，我帮您介绍一个人吧\N{\rEng}I can introduce you to another guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,用不着你介绍，我自己没人吗？\N{\rEng}No need for that! I've got lots of guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,要信得过才成嘛\N{\rEng}I must find one that is reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:44.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,自己兄弟，帮还是不帮？\N{\rEng}Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:49.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,就算现在我换人帮我，这件事你已经知道了\N{\rEng}Even if I find others, you've known this case already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:54.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,以后出了漏子，你洗也洗不清啊！\N{\rEng}If there's anything wrong later, you'll be suspected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,就勉为其难吧\N{\rEng}Don't refuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:08.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看你这儿生意还不错嘛\N{\rEng}Your business is good here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,有没有人来闹事啊？\N{\rEng}Got any guy making trouble here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,有的话，告诉我一声啊\N{\rEng}Tell me if there is any!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:19.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢啊！\N{\rEng}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,还生我气啊？\N{\rEng}Still be angry about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么意思啊？\N{\rEng}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,送给你的\N{\rEng}It's for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不是说好喜欢这条链子吗？\N{\rEng}Haven't you said that you liked it very much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,赌钱赢回来的我不要\N{\rEng}I won't take it if it was won from gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,别这么小器\N{\rEng}Don't be childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:57.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，来，你过来！\N{\rEng}Rick, come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:02.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么事，张伯？\N{\rEng}What's the matter, Uncle Cheung?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,坐！\N{\rEng}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么了？又跟阿立赌气？\N{\rEng}Quarreling again with Lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,迁就她嘛\N{\rEng}She is spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的\N{\rEng}Just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:15.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，我有点事请你帮帮忙\N{\rEng}Rick, I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\rEng}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:18.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想让你给我开车\N{\rEng}I want you to be my driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,开车！\N{\rEng}Driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,没问题，什么时候？\N{\rEng}No problem! When?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能会有危险\N{\rEng}There maybe danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,帮一个人偷渡过来\N{\rEng}We'll help a guy immigrate illegally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:31.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,您张伯的事，没问题，我帮你\N{\rEng}I'll do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:32.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,那谢了！\N{\rEng}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,刚才我爸跟你说什么？\N{\rEng}What did my dad talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,没什么，我拒绝他了\N{\rEng}I rejected his proposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,拒绝？拒绝他什么？\N{\rEng}What have you rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:53.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,拒绝你啦！他让我娶你\N{\rEng}I refused to marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,你美丽动人，活泼可爱\N{\rEng}You're beautiful and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,温柔体贴，天真无邪，准有帮人运\N{\rEng}So kind that you'll bring luck to husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,可惜我没有福气啊\N{\rEng}But I don't have that luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:11.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,链子啊链子，你可真没用了\N{\rEng}This chain has no use now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:12.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,人家都不要你\N{\rEng}No one need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,你滚蛋吧\N{\rEng}Just go away, stupid chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,你干吗扔掉它？\N{\rEng}Why did you throw it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不管，你给我捡回来\N{\rEng}Pick it back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,不认识我啦？\N{\rEng}Don't you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,越大越漂亮啦\N{\rEng}Getting prettier every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,你爸爸在家啊\N{\rEng}Is your dad home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,老张，好久不见，好吗？\N{\rEng}Long time no see, Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,这里还不错\N{\rEng}It's not bad here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:15.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,生意过得去吧？\N{\rEng}How is your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:16.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,还过得去…\N{\rEng}So so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:26.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,找得我这么急，有什么好关照啊？\N{\rEng}Why looking for me in such an urgency?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,还不是老买卖\N{\rEng}Old trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不是跟我说上岸了吗？\N{\rEng}Wasn't you retired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,帮个朋友吧！\N{\rEng}I'm helping a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,这不是上水吗？\N{\rEng}Isn't here Sheung Shui?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,再过去就是元朗啦\N{\rEng}We'll be in Yuen Long soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道，跟着是青山\N{\rEng}Then it is Castle Peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后是荃湾，葵涌了\N{\rEng}And then Tsuen Wan, Kwai Chung.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,张伯，有邓丽君的带子吗？放来听听\N{\rEng}Do you have any audio-tape of Theresa Tang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:03.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是总督牌，美国的嘛\N{\rEng}This is Viceroy, an American brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:12.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我早就抽过了\N{\rEng}I've smoked that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在我换牌子，抽万宝路啦\N{\rEng}Now I'm a Malboro man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,香港特区也不现代化\N{\rEng}Hong Kong is not that modern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:20.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,跟深圳差不多\N{\rEng}Similar to Shenzhen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:22.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,张伯，你这辆车有空调吗？\N{\rEng}Does this car have air-conditioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爸爸的“宾司”有空调的\N{\rEng}My dad's Benz has air-conditioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,小老弟，挺机灵的吧\N{\rEng}Young man, you're smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你来香港一定混得起来\N{\rEng}You'll succeed in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:37.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么？有没有想过干点什么？\N{\rEng}Haven't you thought of doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想当歌星，举行演唱会\N{\rEng}I want to be a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,红磡有个体育馆嘛\N{\rEng}Singing in a concert at the Hong Kong Coliseum
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,以后我就要在那儿唱\N{\rEng}some days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,有志气\N{\rEng}Good ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,不过当歌星要有门路\N{\rEng}But you got to have connection to be a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,小意思，我老爸一句话就成了\N{\rEng}I'll make it with the help of my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,你老爸是李嘉诚啊？\N{\rEng}Who's he? Lee Ka-shing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,我老爸不是李嘉诚\N{\rEng}No, he isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,罗万成啊\N{\rEng}He's Law Man-shing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,听说过吧\N{\rEng}Haven't you heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,干什么？你干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,有警察！\N{\rEng}Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:38.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,兄弟，自己人，带他回总部\N{\rEng}Take him to the headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 自己人啊，开车吧  - 谢谢\N{\rEng}- Ok!  - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,高招啊！\N{\rEng}Clever trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:57.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,老张，咱们喝点东西吧？\N{\rEng}Let's have some drinks, Cheung?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,赶时间啊\N{\rEng}We're in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,还不放开我？\N{\rEng}Release me then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:04.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,也不急在这一会儿，对吧？\N{\rEng}There's no need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:11.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,老弟，在前面杂货铺停下\N{\rEng}Young man, stop before the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,正好，我想喝水\N{\rEng}Good, I'm thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,别那么用力，很痛啊\N{\rEng}Be gentle. It's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:36.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，下来喝点汽水\N{\rEng}Rick, come and have some drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用了，我在车上等就行了\N{\rEng}No, thanks! I wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,麻烦你，两瓶汽水\N{\rEng}Two bottles of soft drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\rEng}Release me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:06.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,老张，这可是你不对了\N{\rEng}Cheung, you're too selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:09.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,罗万成的儿子，你居然不告诉我\N{\rEng}Why don't you tell me that he's Law's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,这可是财神爷，你给得这么少？\N{\rEng}He's wealthy but you give me so little!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,还不带我找我爸爸？\N{\rEng}Why don't you take me to my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,张伯，你快带我去啊\N{\rEng}Take me to my dad at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:24.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,你还在这儿等什么？\N{\rEng}What are you still waiting for here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想要多少呢？\N{\rEng}How much do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,至少这个数\N{\rEng}At least this figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,老张，你给我听着啊\N{\rEng}Cheung, you listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果捞不到什么油水的话\N{\rEng}If I didn't get any benefit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我宁愿把他献上去领功请赏\N{\rEng}I'd rather arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧，见了成哥，我跟他说\N{\rEng}Ok, I tell Shing when I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:08.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在说好一点\N{\rEng}It's better to tell him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:15.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,来\N{\rEng}Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,小老弟，再忍耐一会儿吧\N{\rEng}Young man, be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂，成哥，我是老张\N{\rEng}Hello, Brother Shing! It's me, Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,你儿子没事\N{\rEng}Your son is alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我这位兄弟手头儿有点紧\N{\rEng}The cop here wants more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:43.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,请您加点\N{\rEng}Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:45.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,没问题吧？\N{\rEng}Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,好…\N{\rEng}Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,我这个…\N{\rEng}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:05.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,好啊，耍我是吗？\N{\rEng}Trying to fool me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,有你的，妈的，胆敢耍我！\N{\rEng}You cunning old fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,邓Sir，我不是这个意思\N{\rEng}Tang, I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是怕把事情弄糟了\N{\rEng}I don't want to foul it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,你还说没有耍我？\N{\rEng}Aren't you fooling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,你信不信我把他带到警局\N{\rEng}I'll arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,谁也没便宜的\N{\rEng}None of us will benefit from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:21.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,邓Sir，你听我说…\N{\rEng}Tang, please listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,你妈的耍浪头？好，我就陪你玩\N{\rEng}Don't you try to play tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,我现在马上把他带到警察局\N{\rEng}I take him to the police station now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看你怎么跟成哥交代\N{\rEng}I wonder what you can say to Big Brother Shing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:28.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是…\N{\rEng}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:33.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,你他妈的耍我？我就让你耍到底\N{\rEng}I call the cards now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:39.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,邓Sir，你不要逼我，实际上我是…\N{\rEng}Tang, don't drive me too far please! I, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,你他妈的胆敢抢枪？\N{\rEng}You chicken shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,邓Sir，你为什么要开枪？\N{\rEng}Tang, you are in a big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:06.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,别动！\N{\rEng}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:08.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,你叫我怎么跟罗万成交代啊\N{\rEng}How can I explain to Big Brother Shing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,交代？\N{\rEng}Explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:47.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,爸！\N{\rEng}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立，快上车！\N{\rEng}Lap, get into the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我打电话给老王，你在车上等我\N{\rEng}I'll phone Wong! Wait for me in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列呢？\N{\rEng}Where's Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:53.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,他在码头等我们\N{\rEng}He's waiting at the pier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 发生什么事？ - 上车再说\N{\rEng}- What happened?  - Just get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂，老王！\N{\rEng}Hello, Wong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,有没有船？\N{\rEng}Have you got any ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊！\N{\rEng}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,出了事啦，要避一避\N{\rEng}Something is wrong! We have to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:11.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,三个人，越快越好\N{\rEng}Three! As soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,爸！\N{\rEng}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:45.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立，你要上哪儿去？\N{\rEng}Lap, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我去报警啊！\N{\rEng}I call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:52.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不能去，这种事可不能报警啊！\N{\rEng}You can't report this case to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我怎么办呢？\N{\rEng}Then what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,快点找人救你爸爸！\N{\rEng}Find someone to save your dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,我找谁啊？\N{\rEng}Whom could I ask for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,找神爷！\N{\rEng}Find Godfather Shen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:02.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷？\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:05.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊，你爸爸以前跟他合作\N{\rEng}Yes, he was your dad's partner once
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看他说不定会帮你\N{\rEng}I think he may help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:58.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,请问神爷在吗？\N{\rEng}Is Godfather Shen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:19:59.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,找神爷干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you looking him for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:02.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,我找他有要事，他在吗？\N{\rEng}Something urgent. Is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷！\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:41.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,全都湿透啦，偷渡游过来吗？\N{\rEng}All wet! Stowing away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:46.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,来，坐下来，慢慢说\N{\rEng}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是张海棠的女儿，我爸爸出事了\N{\rEng}I'm Cheung's daughter. He's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:53.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,想找你帮忙救他\N{\rEng}Would you help me save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是张伯的女儿啊\N{\rEng}You're Cheung's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,以前我见过你啊\N{\rEng}I'd seen you before
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,脱光了衣服，在家洗澡的时候\N{\rEng}You were bathing naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我还拧过你的屁股呢\N{\rEng}I caressed you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,把你给弄哭了\N{\rEng}and you cried!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,幸亏你爸爸不在家\N{\rEng}It was lucky that your dad wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是说起张伯他…\N{\rEng}Talking about Uncle Cheung...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爸爸让罗万成抓去了\N{\rEng}My dad was taken by Big Brother Shing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,先喝杯茶\N{\rEng}Have some tea first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:17.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,来，慢慢说，叙旧嘛，干吗那么焦急？\N{\rEng}Why so hurry! Speak slowly and calmly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:29.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,你可否帮我把我爸爸救出来？\N{\rEng}Would you help me save my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:35.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,张伯的事我也听说了\N{\rEng}I've heard about Cheung's case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:38.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,至于谁对谁错，我不管\N{\rEng}I don't care who's right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:42.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,罗万成这个人很难对付，谁都知道的\N{\rEng}But everyone knows that Big Brother Shing is a tough one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,在道上要讲规矩\N{\rEng}We have rules to obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会帮自己的弟兄\N{\rEng}We have to help our own men!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:50.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我找不到什么理由帮你啊\N{\rEng}But I find no reason to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:06.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,漂亮小妞就不同了\N{\rEng}But there's exception for beautiful girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,有两种女人，我一定要帮\N{\rEng}There are two kinds of women that I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.61,0:22:11.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,要么是我老妈，要么是我马子\N{\rEng}One is my mother and the others are my whores.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,你跟我老妈沾不上边啦\N{\rEng}You are not my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:18.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,求我帮你，就是我马子啦\N{\rEng}So you have to be my whore if you want me to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:21.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,你他妈的\N{\rEng}Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:23.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷！\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:28.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不是来找我吗？\N{\rEng}Aren't you coming for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么没见面就走？\N{\rEng}Why leaving so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,她是张海棠的女儿\N{\rEng}She is Cheung's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:38.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道，这么有性格，你让她去陪客\N{\rEng}I know! And you treat her as a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:39.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是大材小用了吗？\N{\rEng}How tasteless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.45,0:22:44.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看得起你，给你一个机会跟着我\N{\rEng}I am offering you this chance to be my woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:46.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,你认为怎么样？\N{\rEng}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:58.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,好好的考虑考虑，千万不要勉强\N{\rEng}Think carefully! I won't force you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:04.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,罗万成那个老小子，够阴险的\N{\rEng}Big Brother Shing is bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:06.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,张伯这次算是倒霉了\N{\rEng}Cheung is in a great trouble this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:08.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,掉在他的手里\N{\rEng}Once in his hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,随时会没命\N{\rEng}no chance of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:14.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,张伯的年纪那么大了，熬不过啊\N{\rEng}Cheung's too old. He can't survive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,这老命八成要玩完啊\N{\rEng}Chances are he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:19.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,就算捡回一条命，也好受不到哪儿去\N{\rEng}He'll suffer a lot even if he is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:22.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,再来个断手断脚的，这辈子就交待啦\N{\rEng}He may lose one of his legs or arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是临老走霉运\N{\rEng}Bloody old fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:28.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷！\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.96,0:23:45.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列！\N{\rEng}Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.06,0:23:52.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么才来啊？没事吧？\N{\rEng}Why are you so late? Is it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:54.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,你爸爸呢？\N{\rEng}Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:23:59.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,他来不了\N{\rEng}He can't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:04.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,不过你不用担心，有人罩着他\N{\rEng}But don't worry! He's under protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:09.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爸爸叫你先走，他不会有事的\N{\rEng}He wants you to leave! He's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:10.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,那你呢？\N{\rEng}Then what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.93,0:24:12.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要留下来陪我爸爸\N{\rEng}I'll stay here with dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:14.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,待我办妥了这儿的事，会过来找你\N{\rEng}I'll come to you after I've finished the work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:16.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,别忘了写信给我！\N{\rEng}Don't forget to write me letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我也不走了！\N{\rEng}Then I won't leave either!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.33,0:24:22.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行，警察查到你的车，正在通缉你\N{\rEng}No way! The police learned of your license plate number.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:24.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,你一定要走\N{\rEng}You must leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.16,0:24:26.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,你放心，我们不会有事\N{\rEng}We'll be alright! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.27,0:24:38.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,先吃饭吧，船快来了\N{\rEng}Have some food first! The ship will come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.73,0:24:39.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,这么快？\N{\rEng}So soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.57,0:24:43.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊，王伯已经安排好了\N{\rEng}Yes, Uncle Wong had arranged everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.27,0:24:46.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，你穿的衣服，要用的东西\N{\rEng}Rick, here're clothes and other things
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.97,0:24:48.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我全替你收拾好了\N{\rEng}that I prepared for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.54,0:25:03.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,慢慢吃嘛，还有时间呢，小心噎着\N{\rEng}Take it easy! There's still time!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.94,0:25:20.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\rEng}Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.07,0:25:23.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有！\N{\rEng}Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.71,0:25:26.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在担心，你一个人走那么远\N{\rEng}I'm worrying that you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.87,0:25:30.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,放心吧，阿立，这算不了什么！\N{\rEng}Don't worry! I can handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.21,0:25:33.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我这么聪明，到哪儿都混得起来\N{\rEng}I'm smart enough to survive at anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.94,0:25:45.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,好好照顾自己啊！\N{\rEng}Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.04,0:25:49.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,你也是！\N{\rEng}You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.02,0:26:22.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,待会儿穿上这件大衣\N{\rEng}Put on this overcoat later!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.62,0:26:24.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,出了海，风会很大的\N{\rEng}The wind is strong in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.52,0:26:36.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列…\N{\rEng}Rick...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.76,0:26:55.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,告诉你爸，我走了\N{\rEng}Say goodbye for me to your dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.22,0:27:06.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列！\N{\rEng}Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.26,0:27:13.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,快过来，我等你\N{\rEng}Come over! I wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.59,0:27:16.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,别逼我娶菲律宾妞儿啊！\N{\rEng}I don't want to marry a Pilipino woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.80,0:28:03.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,这么早就来了，祥老大\N{\rEng}Big Brother Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.20,0:28:04.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,别糗我了，良哥\N{\rEng}Don't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.90,0:28:15.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,立姐，祥哥！\N{\rEng}Miss Lap, Mr. Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.47,0:28:20.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,大小姐！\N{\rEng}Miss Lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.37,0:28:35.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,爸，你又喝酒？\N{\rEng}Dad, are you drinking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.07,0:28:36.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已经叫你不要喝了\N{\rEng}I've told you not to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.81,0:28:39.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,不喝酒，还叫我干什么？\N{\rEng}What else can I do if I don't drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.31,0:28:49.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,不要给他酒，给他参茶\N{\rEng}Don't give him liquor. Give him Ginseng tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.81,0:28:54.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立，今天让我喝一次嘛\N{\rEng}Let me drink another cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.38,0:28:56.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,不许喝！\N{\rEng}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.24,0:29:00.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是不是太过份了？\N{\rEng}Am I driving him too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.01,0:29:02.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你也是为他好嘛\N{\rEng}You're doing that for his good!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.21,0:29:03.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,他前几天刚刚洗完胃\N{\rEng}He had his stomach washed just a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.51,0:29:05.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,医生都叫他不要再喝酒了\N{\rEng}The doctor had told him not to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.98,0:29:08.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,你替我看着他\N{\rEng}Look after him for me please!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.52,0:29:27.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立，过来…来\N{\rEng}Lap, come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.92,0:29:29.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,我给你介绍几位日本大老板\N{\rEng}Let me introduce you to some Japanese tycoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.05,0:29:33.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,我来介绍，这位是田中先生\N{\rEng}This is Mr. Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.78,0:29:35.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,您好，干杯！\N{\rEng}How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.78,0:29:42.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,这位是山本先生\N{\rEng}This is Mr. Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.55,0:29:43.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,您好！\N{\rEng}How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.92,0:29:48.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,干杯！\N{\rEng}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.55,0:29:58.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,这位是西都先生\N{\rEng}This is Mr. Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.12,0:29:59.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,您好！\N{\rEng}How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.79,0:30:31.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,给我一杯酒，阿祥！\N{\rEng}Give me some liquor, Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.26,0:30:33.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,想喝酒吗，张伯？\N{\rEng}Do you want a drink, Uncle Cheung?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.36,0:30:40.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,来，这是孝敬您的\N{\rEng}This one is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.49,0:30:42.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立姐说，不能让他喝\N{\rEng}Miss Lap said that he could not drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.89,0:30:45.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,是吗？你听见没有？\N{\rEng}Really! Haven't you heard of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.86,0:30:48.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,你女儿多疼你啊，叫你别喝啦\N{\rEng}Your daughter loves you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.46,0:30:50.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立说说罢了\N{\rEng}She didn't mean what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.83,0:30:51.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,你真的这么想喝酒啊？\N{\rEng}Do you really want to drink so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.86,0:30:52.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,料哥！\N{\rEng}Brother Liu!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.46,0:31:02.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,不如这样，你蹲下来\N{\rEng}Why don't you kneel down
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.23,0:31:04.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,藏在我下边，我倒给你喝！\N{\rEng}and hide under me? I pour the drink to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.30,0:31:06.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,你女儿不就看不见了吗\N{\rEng}Then your daughter won't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.97,0:31:08.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,好…\N{\rEng}Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.53,0:31:13.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,料哥！\N{\rEng}Brother Liu!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.73,0:31:21.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,好酒量…\N{\rEng}You can drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.64,0:31:35.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,张开嘴！\N{\rEng}Open your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.67,0:31:44.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,好喝吧\N{\rEng}Taste good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.67,0:31:54.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,不但人漂亮，唱得更好\N{\rEng}She is a beauty and a drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.01,0:32:09.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,我唱得不好，请多多包涵\N{\rEng}I sang poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.73,0:34:16.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,张伯，不如走吧！\N{\rEng}Uncle Cheung, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.80,0:34:19.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立！\N{\rEng}Lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.03,0:34:21.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我回去陪您喝好吗？\N{\rEng}Let me drink with you at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.80,0:34:26.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,好…\N{\rEng}Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.80,0:34:27.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,来…\N{\rEng}Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.91,0:35:27.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，好久不见，干杯！\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen, long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.78,0:35:28.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,干杯！\N{\rEng}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.31,0:35:32.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,坐下来慢慢聊嘛\N{\rEng}Please sit down and talk awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.81,0:35:33.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,好！\N{\rEng}Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.44,0:35:39.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,你那位搭挡刘胖子的事情怎么样了？\N{\rEng}How's thing going with your partner, Fat Lau?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.54,0:35:40.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,没牵连到你吧？\N{\rEng}Would it give you any trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.75,0:35:44.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,应该不会，他很够意思\N{\rEng}I don't think it would! He won't do any harm to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.31,0:35:46.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,不对吧！\N{\rEng}No, he isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.41,0:35:48.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我最近收到风声\N{\rEng}I've heard that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.31,0:35:50.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,他已经变成警方的污点证人\N{\rEng}he's turned police's witness now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.05,0:35:53.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,还打算把你的事情全都说出来了\N{\rEng}He's going to tell all the things about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.51,0:35:55.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,并且要干掉你啊\N{\rEng}And he's going to finish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.65,0:36:00.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,还是小心一点好！\N{\rEng}You'd better watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.65,0:36:03.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，我要干掉你\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen, I'll finish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.35,0:36:10.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,没事…他不小心摔了一跤\N{\rEng}It's alright... He tumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.82,0:36:13.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,没事…\N{\rEng}It's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.12,0:36:15.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,车就停在那边\N{\rEng}The car is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.49,0:36:17.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不要坐神爷的车\N{\rEng}I don't want to take Godfather Shen's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.05,0:36:19.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,好…我们坐计程车好吗？\N{\rEng}Ok! We'll take a taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.25,0:36:22.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,好啦，你进去看着阿立\N{\rEng}You go to look after Lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.02,0:36:24.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我先送你回去\N{\rEng}I take you home first!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.32,0:36:30.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,我没事，你进去看着阿立吧，我没事\N{\rEng}I'm alright. Go look after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.29,0:36:34.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,张伯，你真的没事吧？\N{\rEng}Uncle Cheung, are you really alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.29,0:37:19.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,你马上给我找个可靠的人\N{\rEng}Find me a reliable man at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.66,0:37:23.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,趁刘胖子出庭之前杀了他\N{\rEng}and go to kill Fat Lau before he goes to the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.43,0:37:25.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,千万不能失手\N{\rEng}No failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.73,0:37:27.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,好！\N{\rEng}Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.04,0:38:16.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,来一杯Vodka Tonic\N{\rEng}Give me a glass of Vodka Tonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.14,0:38:32.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,先生，谢谢二十块\N{\rEng}20 dollars, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.54,0:38:37.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢！\N{\rEng}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.51,0:38:47.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，你好\N{\rEng}Dear Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.04,0:38:52.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,香港很冷，不知道你那边怎么样\N{\rEng}Hong Kong is cold! How's the weather in Philippine?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.94,0:38:59.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，你说你已经全都安顿好了\N{\rEng}You've told me that you'd settled down already,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.65,0:39:02.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且已经开始适应那边的生活了\N{\rEng}and began to adapt to the lifestyle there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.68,0:39:04.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我就放心了\N{\rEng}I was happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.08,0:39:08.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爸已经没事了\N{\rEng}Dad was alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.28,0:39:10.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,酒吧也让给人家了\N{\rEng}But the bar was sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.78,0:39:13.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,一切好像要重新再来一样\N{\rEng}We seemed to have to start all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.31,0:39:18.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,你问我何时到菲律宾找你\N{\rEng}You asked me when I would come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.35,0:39:22.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的答案会让你很失望\N{\rEng}My answer may upset you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.78,0:39:26.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已经决定不过去了\N{\rEng}I've decided not coming to Philippine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.68,0:39:30.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,你走了之后\N{\rEng}After your leaving,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.05,0:39:33.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我曾经冷静想过\N{\rEng}I've thought calmly and thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.35,0:39:36.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,其实我们的性格有很大的不同\N{\rEng}There's a great difference between our personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.05,0:39:41.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,干脆趁着这个机会，大家算啦\N{\rEng}We'd better break up, seizing this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.99,0:39:43.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,无谓再拖下去了\N{\rEng}It's worthless to carry on such a relation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.12,0:39:47.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,希望你安心在那边发展\N{\rEng}Wish you have a stable living and development.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.45,0:39:53.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,不要再惦记我，好好保重\N{\rEng}Just forget me and take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.19,0:39:54.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立\N{\rEng}Yours sincerely, Lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.80,0:40:48.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起，忘了拿打火机\N{\rEng}Sorry, I've forgot my lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.07,0:41:14.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，你喜欢这里吗？\N{\rEng}Do you like this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.07,0:41:18.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,这儿不错啊\N{\rEng}Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.10,0:41:19.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,以前这儿更好\N{\rEng}This place was better in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.67,0:41:21.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,以前是我爸爸开的\N{\rEng}My dad ran this place before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.24,0:41:25.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,那时候我很开心的\N{\rEng}I was very happy at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.77,0:41:27.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你现在也蛮好的\N{\rEng}You're living fine now also.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.27,0:41:32.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你小时候开不开心？\N{\rEng}Did you enjoy your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.91,0:41:37.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然开心了，我外婆很疼我的\N{\rEng}Of course, my grandma loved me very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.21,0:41:38.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,那个时候我喜欢看电影\N{\rEng}I liked watching movie very much at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.61,0:41:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,她知道我没钱，假装让我陪她看\N{\rEng}She knew I had no money so she pretended to watch movie
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.07,0:41:43.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,她是为了满足我\N{\rEng}and asked me to come with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.84,0:41:45.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,一进电影院她就睡着了\N{\rEng}But she felt asleep at the minute she went into the cinema.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.24,0:41:47.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,你外婆还在不在？\N{\rEng}Is you grandma still living?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.94,0:41:50.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,在，不过她老了\N{\rEng}She is still living, but very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.08,0:41:56.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，你活到这么大\N{\rEng}Cheung, after all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.88,0:41:58.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,有没有真正喜欢一个人？\N{\rEng}have you really loved any one?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.91,0:42:07.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,即使说有，你也不会相信\N{\rEng}You won't believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.55,0:42:24.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,还想着以前的男朋友？\N{\rEng}Are you thinking of your past boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.25,0:42:29.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,算了，立姐，你们这么多年没见，什么都变了\N{\rEng}Everything must have changed after so many years of departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.78,0:42:35.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不会明白\N{\rEng}You won't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.38,0:42:38.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你真的喜欢一个人\N{\rEng}If you really love someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.52,0:42:41.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,你会永远想着他\N{\rEng}you'll think of him forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.32,0:42:45.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,既然如此，你过去找他吧\N{\rEng}Then you would go to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.32,0:42:47.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么找？\N{\rEng}Where could I find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.75,0:42:55.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,算了，立姐，还是忘了他吧\N{\rEng}Just forget him!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.72,0:42:59.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,他人真的很好\N{\rEng}He's really quite a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.32,0:43:04.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,这条链子就是他送给我的\N{\rEng}This is the bracelet he gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.32,0:43:05.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,我一直戴到现在\N{\rEng}I'm wearing it until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.89,0:43:09.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,你可不要告诉神爷啊\N{\rEng}You mustn't tell Godfather Shen about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.49,0:43:12.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真想看看他到底长成什么样子\N{\rEng}I really want to know how he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.89,0:43:14.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,你把他夸得这么好\N{\rEng}You've said so many good words about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.72,0:43:15.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的有点嫉妒\N{\rEng}I am really jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.39,0:43:19.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,不，当我没说过\N{\rEng}No, I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.99,0:43:24.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，如果我有机会再见他\N{\rEng}If I could meet him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.32,0:43:26.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我一定会跟他走\N{\rEng}I would leave with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.46,0:43:28.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,那时候你会不会帮我？\N{\rEng}Would you help me leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.86,0:43:31.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,到时候再说吧\N{\rEng}I don't know. Let's wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.23,0:43:33.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,会不会帮我？\N{\rEng}Would you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.23,0:43:38.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.26,0:43:40.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你会帮我的\N{\rEng}You will.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.56,0:43:45.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,都这么多年了\N{\rEng}After all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.63,0:43:48.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,说不定人家结了婚，生了孩子呢\N{\rEng}he might have married already.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.03,0:44:04.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,四点开庭，这么早就他妈去\N{\rEng}The court hold at 4! Why so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.70,0:44:07.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,早知道那么麻烦，我就不做证人了\N{\rEng}I wouldn't be the witness if I knew it's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.33,0:44:12.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,这次麻烦你，拜托帮帮忙！\N{\rEng}Please give us a hand, Mr. Lau!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.43,0:44:14.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是看在曹警司份上\N{\rEng}If not because of lnspector Tso,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.40,0:44:16.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,跪下求我，我也不去啊！\N{\rEng}I won't go even if you kneel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.77,0:44:58.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,开车！\N{\rEng}Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.84,0:45:09.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,你什么时候回来的？\N{\rEng}When were you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.54,0:45:10.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,昨天晚上\N{\rEng}Last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.18,0:45:13.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,你刚才这么匆忙，有事吗？\N{\rEng}Why were you in such a hurry just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.98,0:45:15.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我今天就走\N{\rEng}I'm leaving today.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.04,0:45:18.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,去哪儿？回菲律宾？\N{\rEng}Where will you go? Philippine?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.48,0:45:22.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,你现在去哪儿？我送你！\N{\rEng}Where are you going? I'll give you a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.98,0:45:25.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在前面下车\N{\rEng}Could I get off at there?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.01,0:45:27.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列\N{\rEng}Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.11,0:45:30.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,有没有空？我们去喝杯东西\N{\rEng}Let's have a drink, should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.78,0:45:40.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我有事要跟你说\N{\rEng}I have something to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.38,0:45:42.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,说吧！\N{\rEng}Just say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.35,0:45:49.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,没话说吗？\N{\rEng}Nothing to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.12,0:45:54.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,其实你要说的，这封信已经全说了\N{\rEng}Actually what you want to say is all written in this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.55,0:45:55.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,还给你\N{\rEng}Take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.09,0:46:51.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 喂  - 马列吗？\N{\rEng}- Hello!  - Is it Rick Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.19,0:46:53.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.19,0:46:55.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是阿料，今晚行程有变动吗？\N{\rEng}It's Liu. Is there any change in tonight's schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.43,0:46:56.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.46,0:46:58.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我们准时在菜市码头见\N{\rEng}Then we'll meet on time at the pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.23,0:47:00.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.66,0:47:18.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我可否进来？ - 我赶时间\N{\rEng}- Can I come in?  - I have no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.40,0:47:20.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,你放心，我不会耽误你很久\N{\rEng}Don't worry, I won't take you too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.23,0:47:31.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，我知道这几年你过得不容易\N{\rEng}Rick, I know you suffered a lot all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.23,0:47:32.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,我怎么过与你无关\N{\rEng}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.27,0:47:36.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，对不起！\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.17,0:47:37.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,用不着说对不起\N{\rEng}There's no need to say sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.23,0:47:38.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,你没什么对不起我的\N{\rEng}You have done nothing to be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.73,0:47:40.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道我没去找你，你生我的气\N{\rEng}You're angry because I didn't come to you, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.03,0:47:42.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,都过去啦！\N{\rEng}What was done was done!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.37,0:47:45.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.27,0:47:49.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,你回去吧，时间到了，我该走了\N{\rEng}It's time for you to go back! And me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.54,0:47:55.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,没想到我等了这么久\N{\rEng}I've been waiting for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.44,0:47:57.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,你连一个机会都不给我\N{\rEng}but you didn't give me a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.37,0:47:59.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你等我？\N{\rEng}Were you waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.64,0:48:01.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,当初我走的时候，你答应过我什么？\N{\rEng}What had you promised me when I was leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.67,0:48:03.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在那边等了这么久，我又等到什么？\N{\rEng}What had I got then by waiting there for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.01,0:48:05.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,你听我说！\N{\rEng}Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.87,0:48:09.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,算了，阿立，谁对谁错根本没有意义\N{\rEng}It's meaningless to discuss who's right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.14,0:48:11.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,即使你不想听，我也要说\N{\rEng}You must listen to me even if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.04,0:48:15.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,出事那天晚上，我爸爸被罗万成抓了\N{\rEng}That night at the accident, my dad was caught by Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.21,0:48:18.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,为了救爸爸，我去找神爷\N{\rEng}I went to Godfather Shen to ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.27,0:48:19.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我没告诉你\N{\rEng}I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.67,0:48:22.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,是怕你留下来不肯走，怕你出事\N{\rEng}I didn't want you to stay and get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.74,0:48:25.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷答应帮我，但是要我跟他\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen promised to help if I agreed to follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.98,0:48:28.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,为了救我爸，我没法子不跟他\N{\rEng}For the sake of dad, I had to agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.94,0:48:30.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷这个人不简单\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen is a man of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.81,0:48:33.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道这辈子我们不能在一起了\N{\rEng}I knew we'd never stay together
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.38,0:48:36.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,我写信给你，是让你死了这条心\N{\rEng}so I wrote to you to change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.28,0:48:38.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不希望你再这么等下去\N{\rEng}I didn't want you to wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.64,0:48:40.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,我虽然人跟着神爷\N{\rEng}Although I lived with Godfather Shen,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.64,0:48:43.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我的心一直想着你\N{\rEng}I thought of you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.48,0:48:45.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,这几年来，我过得很乱\N{\rEng}In these years, my life is chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.78,0:48:50.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,爸最近去世了，我才开始有点希望\N{\rEng}My dad died recently and my life starts to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.15,0:48:51.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我好想去找你\N{\rEng}I want to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.01,0:48:55.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,刚才碰见你，我很开心\N{\rEng}I was very happy when I met you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.68,0:48:57.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,以为我们可以再在一起了\N{\rEng}I thought we could stay together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.75,0:49:03.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能已经过去了，真的不能再回头\N{\rEng}Maybe time passed could never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.42,0:49:08.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，你保重！\N{\rEng}Rick, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.93,0:50:09.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,出门啊？\N{\rEng}Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.99,0:50:13.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么事啊？\N{\rEng}Do you have business to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.16,0:50:21.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,什么事啊？\N{\rEng}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.66,0:50:23.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好急吗？赶时间啊？\N{\rEng}Are you in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.36,0:50:28.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,我刚刚有空，特地上来看看你嘛\N{\rEng}I was free just now so I come to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.40,0:50:31.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起，我没时间，你自己慢慢坐吧\N{\rEng}Sorry, I have no time to stay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.10,0:50:35.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,不至于吧，聊几句都没空吗？\N{\rEng}Don't you have time for just a few words?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.17,0:50:38.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想怎么样？\N{\rEng}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.63,0:50:41.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果让神爷知道的话，他怎么想？\N{\rEng}What will Godfather Shen do if he knows this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.97,0:50:43.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我可得问问他啦\N{\rEng}Then I must ask him for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.57,0:50:46.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我打个电话问问他\N{\rEng}I must phone him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.47,0:50:53.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,料哥，这么认真干吗？开玩笑嘛\N{\rEng}Don't take it so serious? I was only joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.60,0:50:57.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也是开玩笑啊\N{\rEng}I was joking too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.97,0:51:02.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,出来混，大家志在开心，对吗？\N{\rEng}We all want happiness, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.50,0:51:05.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,太认真会伤和气\N{\rEng}We'll spoil everything if we take it too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.70,0:51:10.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,料哥，有什么话就直说吧\N{\rEng}Just say what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.10,0:51:14.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,爽快，我就喜欢你这么有性格\N{\rEng}Straightforward! I like this character of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.21,0:51:21.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱们开门见山\N{\rEng}Ok, let's be frank!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.47,0:51:26.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是赶去码头会情夫？\N{\rEng}Are you going to the pier for your lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.14,0:51:32.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,旧相好吗？\N{\rEng}An old boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.91,0:51:37.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,谁说的，你别听人家乱说，料哥\N{\rEng}Who said that? Stop bullshitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.54,0:51:39.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是去旅行\N{\rEng}I am only going for travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.07,0:51:40.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.84,0:51:44.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,对了，你来了这么久，我还没倒茶给你\N{\rEng}I forgot your tea for such a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.04,0:51:47.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们喝杯茶再说吧\N{\rEng}Let's have some time first!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.48,0:51:50.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,这才像话，别老是赶我走\N{\rEng}That's right! Don't always kick me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.51,0:52:11.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,别走！\N{\rEng}Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.38,0:52:17.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,所谓一家便宜两家沾，你想跟他走，我让你走\N{\rEng}I'll let you go if you give me benefit
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.32,0:52:19.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,不会告诉神爷\N{\rEng}and I won't tell Godfather Shen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.12,0:52:21.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,不过，我有什么好处呢？\N{\rEng}But, what can I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.42,0:52:22.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,不知道你胡说什么\N{\rEng}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.35,0:52:25.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,话说得太白就没意思了\N{\rEng}It's no need to say all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.28,0:52:29.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我对你怎么样，咱们大家心照不宣\N{\rEng}You know that I treat you kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.98,0:52:31.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,这件事要是说出来\N{\rEng}If I inform Godfather Shen about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.38,0:52:36.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,别说是你，连他妈那小子也不好受\N{\rEng}you and that guy will be both in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.19,0:52:47.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,乖乖的，大家开心，行吗？\N{\rEng}Let's enjoy a while together, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.86,0:53:11.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,料哥！\N{\rEng}Liu!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.23,0:53:24.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,料哥！\N{\rEng}Liu!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.13,0:53:26.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,你来得正好，她想溜啊！\N{\rEng}It's good that you've come. She wanted to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.56,0:53:28.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,幸亏让我知道了，及时阻止她\N{\rEng}I just came in time to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.16,0:53:37.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看着她，我打个电话给神爷\N{\rEng}Watch her! I go to call Godfather Shen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.70,0:53:40.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,看着她别让她溜啊\N{\rEng}Keep your eyes on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.63,0:53:47.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,发生什么事啊？\N{\rEng}What happened really?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.23,0:53:53.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列回来了，我要跟他走\N{\rEng}Rick was back, I want to leave with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.27,0:54:00.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂，神爷，赖料啊\N{\rEng}Hello, Godfather Shen. It's Lai Liu speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.27,0:54:02.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，你一定要帮我\N{\rEng}Cheung, you must help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.23,0:54:08.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,有好戏看啦\N{\rEng}Trouble will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.80,0:54:13.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷就在附近，马上到\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen will be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.51,0:55:16.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，坐！\N{\rEng}Please sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.81,0:55:17.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,发生什么事？\N{\rEng}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.31,0:55:21.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立她想…\N{\rEng}She wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.41,0:55:28.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，赖料想强奸我\N{\rEng}Liu wanted to rape me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.68,0:55:31.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有这回事\N{\rEng}It's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.11,0:55:33.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,给我天大的胆子，我也不敢\N{\rEng}I didn't have that guts to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.11,0:55:35.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,她想跟着旧相好跑掉，被我截住了\N{\rEng}She wanted to see her boyfriend but I stopped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.88,0:55:37.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,您看看她，行李都收拾好了\N{\rEng}She had her luggage all packed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.32,0:55:39.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，他胡说！\N{\rEng}He's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.88,0:55:42.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我胡说？那小子，还真巧啦\N{\rEng}That guy... It's really coincident.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.32,0:55:43.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是我们从菲律宾请回来的\N{\rEng}He's the guy employed from Philippine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.08,0:55:45.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,今天我去监视刘胖子\N{\rEng}Today when I kept an eye on Lau,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.92,0:55:48.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,无意中发现那小子是她的旧情人\N{\rEng}I discovered unintentiously about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.95,0:55:52.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立！\N{\rEng}Lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.79,0:55:55.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,有没有这回事？\N{\rEng}Is it the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.39,0:56:05.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,有！\N{\rEng}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.66,0:56:23.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，我已经跟了你那么多年\N{\rEng}I had followed you for so many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.79,0:56:26.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,以前我欠你的，应该还清了\N{\rEng}I had paid you back probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.52,0:56:27.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,就让我走吧！\N{\rEng}Would you let me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.43,0:56:32.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,这次我下了决心要走\N{\rEng}I've decided firmly to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.83,0:56:34.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你那么多女人\N{\rEng}You have so many women.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.09,0:56:36.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,多我一个不多，少我一个也不少啊\N{\rEng}It won't affect you without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.26,0:56:57.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,那小子呢？\N{\rEng}What about that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.90,0:56:59.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,放心吧！\N{\rEng}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.33,0:57:02.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,您吩咐过，事成之后就把他干掉\N{\rEng}You've told me to kill him after the work has finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.33,0:57:03.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我全都布置好了！\N{\rEng}I've already arranged everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.20,0:57:15.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你真的想走？\N{\rEng}Do you really want to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.80,0:57:16.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,对！\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.40,0:57:21.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,既然你的心不在我这儿\N{\rEng}Since you didn't have your heart on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.93,0:57:23.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,我留你也没什么用\N{\rEng}it's no use to make you stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.13,0:57:28.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,不过便宜外人，不如便宜自己弟兄\N{\rEng}But I'd rather benefit my own people.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.67,0:57:30.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿料\N{\rEng}Liu!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.54,0:57:33.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你一直对她很感兴趣\N{\rEng}I know you've been loving her for times.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.67,0:57:43.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我就便宜你了，上啊！\N{\rEng}I'll give you a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.17,0:57:53.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,你简直不是人\N{\rEng}You are not human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.07,0:57:56.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,不错，我是神\N{\rEng}Yes, I'm God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.57,0:57:59.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个世界是我的，你不服气？\N{\rEng}Everybody is under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.27,0:58:04.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿料，还不上！\N{\rEng}Liu, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.31,0:58:18.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,学着点儿，小子！\N{\rEng}Learn a lesson, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.45,0:58:47.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，不要！\N{\rEng}No, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.72,0:58:49.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，你就放了她吧\N{\rEng}Boss, please release her!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.25,0:58:52.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,你神经病啊，把枪放下！\N{\rEng}Are you crazy? Put down the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.75,0:58:56.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我叫你放下枪！\N{\rEng}I told you to put it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.68,0:58:59.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,快走，立姐！\N{\rEng}Go away, be quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.25,0:59:00.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥！\N{\rEng}Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.08,0:59:01.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不想这样的\N{\rEng}I don't mean to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.25,0:59:04.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,不过，你实在太过份了\N{\rEng}But you are driving her too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.42,0:59:05.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,不需要弄出人命嘛\N{\rEng}Don't hurt anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.92,0:59:09.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,她一直对你很好，服侍你这么多年\N{\rEng}She treated you so good for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.12,0:59:10.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就让她走吧\N{\rEng}please let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.35,0:59:11.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,干吗还要逼她呢？\N{\rEng}Why do you have to hurt her still?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.02,0:59:13.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我叫你把枪放下\N{\rEng}Put down the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.55,0:59:18.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，我的手发抖，很容易走火\N{\rEng}I'm trembling and I can't control the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.22,0:59:20.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不想打伤您，您不要逼我\N{\rEng}I may hurt you accidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.69,0:59:21.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,立姐！\N{\rEng}Lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.49,0:59:38.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起，神爷，我不能够不救她\N{\rEng}Sorry, I have to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.36,0:59:41.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,人不能见死不救，是不是？\N{\rEng}I can't stand watching her dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.29,0:59:52.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,立姐！…\N{\rEng}Lap!...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.36,0:59:53.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,快去按电梯\N{\rEng}Get the lift quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.96,0:59:57.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起，神爷！\N{\rEng}Sorry, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.09,1:00:00.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,待我送走立姐，我会回来向你道歉\N{\rEng}After I send her away, I'll be back for your forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.33,1:00:03.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，你胆敢背叛我？\N{\rEng}Don't you dare to betray me?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.06,1:00:05.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有！\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.59,1:00:07.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想救立姐，我没有背叛你\N{\rEng}I just wanted to save her, not to betray you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.06,1:00:09.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，电梯来了\N{\rEng}Cheung, the lift is coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.56,1:00:17.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，别生我气\N{\rEng}Don't be angry about me!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.53,1:00:43.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,他就在里面等你\N{\rEng}He's waiting inside for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.10,1:00:47.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起，阿祥，我连累了你\N{\rEng}Sorry to cause you such a trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.97,1:00:49.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,别这么说，立姐！\N{\rEng}Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.60,1:00:52.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,看见你好，我也开心\N{\rEng}I'm glad to make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.44,1:00:53.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,最重要是你安全\N{\rEng}I worry your safety most.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.54,1:00:57.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,你对我这么好，真不知道怎么感谢你\N{\rEng}You're so kind to me. I didn't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.34,1:01:06.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,你保重！\N{\rEng}Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.77,1:01:08.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,你自己也要小心啊\N{\rEng}You too!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.48,1:01:29.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,你回去吧！\N{\rEng}You should go now!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.25,1:02:00.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列！\N{\rEng}Rick!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.58,1:02:02.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的嘴怎么啦？\N{\rEng}What happened to your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.61,1:02:05.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,没什么，刚才太匆忙，不小心撞了一下\N{\rEng}It's alright! I got hurled carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.29,1:02:25.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,上船吧！\N{\rEng}Get on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.89,1:03:01.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，你怎么样？\N{\rEng}Rick, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.93,1:03:04.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,立姐，你怎么样？\N{\rEng}Lap, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.26,1:03:09.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,别开枪！自己人，是自己人\N{\rEng}Don't shoot! We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.09,1:03:11.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是我朋友\N{\rEng}He's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.89,1:03:21.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,立姐！\N{\rEng}Lap!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.09,1:03:23.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，你怎么还没走？\N{\rEng}Why haven't you left?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.80,1:03:25.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我怕你出事\N{\rEng}I'm worrying about your safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.36,1:03:26.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，你怎么样？\N{\rEng}Rick, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.83,1:03:29.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，快过来帮忙！\N{\rEng}Give me a hand, Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.76,1:03:33.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就是列哥？我叫阿祥\N{\rEng}You must be Rick! I'm Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.76,1:03:35.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我早就听过你的名字\N{\rEng}I've heard about you before.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.06,1:03:38.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,你伤成这样，赶快找医生才行啊\N{\rEng}You're hurt so badly! You must see a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.50,1:03:39.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用了！\N{\rEng}No, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.46,1:03:41.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认识一个大陆医生\N{\rEng}I know a doctor came from China.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.10,1:03:42.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,不要紧，阿祥是自己人\N{\rEng}He's on our side.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.03,1:03:45.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,他怎么样？医生！\N{\rEng}How is he, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.87,1:03:50.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,你叫我彭叔好了，他没什么，不要紧\N{\rEng}Just call me Pang! He's alright!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.10,1:03:53.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,人老了真没用了\N{\rEng}I'm old and useless now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.90,1:03:55.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看看，我把东西都遗留在车上了\N{\rEng}I forgot my tools in the car!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.50,1:03:57.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看着他，我去拿！\N{\rEng}Take care of him! I go to get my tools!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.54,1:04:07.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立，把钥匙交给阿祥，帮我把东西拿来\N{\rEng}Give him the key and tell him to get me something.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.00,1:04:17.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥！\N{\rEng}Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.60,1:04:20.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列想请你帮他拿点东西\N{\rEng}He wanted you to get something for him
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.41,1:04:23.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,在世华会七十六号储物箱里\N{\rEng}at Cabinet no. 76 at Club Siwa.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.71,1:04:27.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,这些让我来做好了\N{\rEng}Let me do these.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.31,1:04:29.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,今天晚上真是谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you so much for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.34,1:04:32.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,别这么客气了，立姐！\N{\rEng}Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.02,1:05:44.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看我这个脑子，又忘了东西\N{\rEng}I forgot my tools again!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.35,1:05:47.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你拿点棉花给他擦伤口，我出去拿东西\N{\rEng}You go to clean his wound with some cotton.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.92,1:06:06.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,你还戴着它\N{\rEng}Why are you still wearing it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.89,1:06:10.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,当时送你你不要，扔了之后，自己又捡回来\N{\rEng}You refused it when I gave you, but picked it back later.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.96,1:06:27.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂，神爷，我是阿彭啊\N{\rEng}Hello, I'm Pang!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.89,1:06:31.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们的人怎么到现在还没有来啊？\N{\rEng}Why didn't your men come still?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.46,1:06:34.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,是…对…\N{\rEng}Yes... Right...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.70,1:06:37.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,好，我尽量拖着他们\N{\rEng}Ok, I try to make them stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.11,1:07:45.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列！\N{\rEng}Rick!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.46,1:09:15.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是这儿？\N{\rEng}Is it here?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.89,1:09:19.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,我下车看看\N{\rEng}I go and see.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.59,1:09:33.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我以前就是在这里打死那个警察\N{\rEng}I had killed a policeman here before.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.66,1:09:38.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列，不要再提以前的事了\N{\rEng}Rick, it's already passed away.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.86,1:09:44.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,想不到又回到这儿\N{\rEng}I came back again now!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.06,1:09:57.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果当初没发生那件事\N{\rEng}If that murder didn't happen,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.86,1:10:00.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,不知道现在会怎么样呢\N{\rEng}I wonder what will become now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.70,1:10:08.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有没有后悔回来？\N{\rEng}Do you regret to come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.13,1:10:13.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,有些事，我从来没后悔过\N{\rEng}I've never regretted on something.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.37,1:10:27.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,里面一个人也没有\N{\rEng}There's no one inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.73,1:10:30.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,看来没人住，我看挺安全的\N{\rEng}I think it's empty and be quite safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.17,1:10:31.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,来，进去吧！\N{\rEng}Let's get in!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.14,1:10:44.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,立姐，别忘了东西\N{\rEng}Don't forget the things!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.21,1:10:52.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我小时候看见外婆生病\N{\rEng}When I was young and saw grandma was ill,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.44,1:10:53.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,就很想当医生\N{\rEng}I wanted to be a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.77,1:10:57.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是想也没想到…\N{\rEng}I don't even imagine that...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.77,1:10:59.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,谁知道以后会发生什么事呢？\N{\rEng}Who knows what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.97,1:11:05.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,列哥，菲律宾有很多杀手，是吗？\N{\rEng}Rick, are there many killers in Philippine?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.74,1:11:10.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,干你们这一行要冷酷无情啊\N{\rEng}You have to be cold blooded in this trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.58,1:11:15.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看得电影太多了…\N{\rEng}You've watched too many movies...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.68,1:11:19.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,那倒不是，起码你们不受人气\N{\rEng}No, actually you are not badly treated.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.18,1:11:23.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷这个人怎么样？\N{\rEng}How is Godfather Shen like?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.51,1:11:29.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,这位老大可难侍候了\N{\rEng}He's difficult to work with.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.28,1:11:31.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你永远都不知道他在想什么\N{\rEng}You never know what he thinks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.48,1:11:35.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真佩服立姐，能忍耐他那么久\N{\rEng}I think Lap is great to have tolerated him for so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.18,1:11:38.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是让我整天对着不喜欢的人\N{\rEng}If I have to face someone I don't like,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.81,1:11:40.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,我情愿死了算了\N{\rEng}I would rather die.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.65,1:11:50.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的伤口好像发炎了\N{\rEng}Your wound seems to be inflamed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.82,1:11:56.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,用刀切开伤口，把子弹弄出来\N{\rEng}Cut the wound and take the bullet out.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.45,1:11:57.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,那可很痛的\N{\rEng}That's painful.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.18,1:12:03.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,来，咬着它\N{\rEng}Bite it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.25,1:12:06.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用了，我承受得来\N{\rEng}No, I can stand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.52,1:12:15.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,就这么弄啊？\N{\rEng}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.69,1:12:20.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？\N{\rEng}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.85,1:12:22.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛\N{\rEng}Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.69,1:12:24.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用，来吧！\N{\rEng}No, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.02,1:12:33.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,干你们这行，可真够绝\N{\rEng}Doing your job must be strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.19,1:12:44.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立，你先出去\N{\rEng}Lap, you go out first.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.89,1:12:48.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要帮忙\N{\rEng}I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.19,1:12:50.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用了，立姐，我一个人可以了\N{\rEng}No, I can manage myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.73,1:13:12.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，你有没有想过将来干什么？\N{\rEng}Cheung, have you thought about your future?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.16,1:13:13.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,光棍儿一条，想什么想？\N{\rEng}No, not worth thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.30,1:13:19.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果有个女人要你照顾呢？\N{\rEng}What if you have a woman to take care of?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.60,1:13:23.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,女人？我外婆啊？\N{\rEng}Woman? My grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.76,1:13:29.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立，万一我出了什么事，你帮我照顾她\N{\rEng}Lap, if I have any accident. Please look after her.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.90,1:13:35.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你答不答应？\N{\rEng}Do you promise?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.30,1:13:38.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,好！\N{\rEng}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.27,1:13:49.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,子弹已经拿出来了\N{\rEng}The bullet is taken out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.28,1:14:51.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,船大概下午可以到达，好！\N{\rEng}The ship will arrive in the afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.01,1:15:06.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂，七二五四一\N{\rEng}725, 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.28,1:15:10.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,你外婆找你，叫你打神爷的手提电话\N{\rEng}Your grandmother told you to call her with Godfather Shen's phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.09,1:15:34.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂，神爷啊！\N{\rEng}Hello, Godfather Shen!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.02,1:15:39.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，你在外边蛮过瘾的吧？\N{\rEng}Cheung, you seem to be enjoying yourself out there!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.79,1:15:43.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,有个人很想念你\N{\rEng}Somebody is missing you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.09,1:15:55.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,喂，阿祥…你留下那么多钱干什么？\N{\rEng}Cheung, why are you leaving so much money?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.86,1:15:57.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,外婆，你怎么样？\N{\rEng}How are you, grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.92,1:16:02.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我没什么，我担心你有什么事\N{\rEng}I'm alright. I'm just worrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.29,1:16:05.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们老板说，你好几天没上班了\N{\rEng}Your boss said you haven't been to work for some days.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.43,1:16:07.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,到底什么事啊？\N{\rEng}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.13,1:16:12.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，阿立呢？\N{\rEng}Cheung, where's Lap?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.99,1:16:13.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道！\N{\rEng}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.29,1:16:16.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,不知道？那算了！\N{\rEng}No? Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.09,1:16:19.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,与我外婆无关，神爷…\N{\rEng}There's nothing to do with my grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.23,1:16:32.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,找我吗？立姐？\N{\rEng}Are you looking for me? Lap?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.76,1:16:35.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起，阿祥！\N{\rEng}Sorry, Cheung!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.53,1:16:37.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,千万别说这些\N{\rEng}Don't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.67,1:16:49.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,外婆在神爷手里？\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen has captured grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.57,1:16:51.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,不要紧，我回去好了\N{\rEng}Never mind. I'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.00,1:16:54.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,没用的，别傻了\N{\rEng}Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.90,1:16:57.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,你已经帮了我这么多\N{\rEng}You've helped me so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.40,1:17:01.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我帮助你并不是为了让你感激我\N{\rEng}I help you not because I want you to feel grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.87,1:17:06.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,快和列哥走吧！\N{\rEng}Run away with Rick!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.67,1:17:09.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,要救外婆出来\N{\rEng}Save grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.97,1:17:12.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷要的是你，不是我外婆\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen wants you, not my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.54,1:17:14.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,你忍耐了那么久，难得有机会跑出来\N{\rEng}It's a valuable chance to have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.74,1:17:16.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,千万不能回去\N{\rEng}Don't go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.77,1:17:20.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，我认识你这么久\N{\rEng}Cheung, I've known you for so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.57,1:17:22.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你对别人友善，我怎么会不知道呢\N{\rEng}I know that you are very nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.81,1:17:26.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,但这次不是小事，神爷会杀了你啊\N{\rEng}This time is different. Godfather Shen will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.47,1:17:28.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,认识这么久，只知道我对别人友善而已？\N{\rEng}You only know that I am nice to others?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.94,1:17:36.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，我知道你的感受\N{\rEng}Cheung, I know what you feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.54,1:17:40.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,你觉得我怎么样？\N{\rEng}What do you think about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.01,1:17:45.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是把我当作是你弟弟啊？\N{\rEng}You only treat me as your brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.98,1:17:49.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊，所以你外婆就是我外婆\N{\rEng}Yes, so your grandmother is my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.44,1:17:54.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,有些事不是你看的那么简单\N{\rEng}Things are not as simple as you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.38,1:18:13.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,喜欢一个人，又不可以跟他在一起，是很痛苦的\N{\rEng}It's painful if you can't be with your loved one.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.91,1:18:17.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.05,1:18:21.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以你要和列哥走，我留下\N{\rEng}So you should go with Rick.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.88,1:18:24.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,就算我肯让你留下，列哥也不会愿意\N{\rEng}Rick won't let you stay either.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.22,1:18:26.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,只要你愿意，我会跟他说\N{\rEng}I'll speak to him if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.45,1:18:28.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥啊…\N{\rEng}Cheung...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.32,1:18:30.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,立姐，我根本没有打算跟你们一起走\N{\rEng}Lap, I never plan to run away with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.72,1:18:34.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们走后，我有办法让神爷慢慢忘记这件事\N{\rEng}I'll make Godfather Shen forget this matter after you leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.75,1:18:38.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,他很照顾我的\N{\rEng}He takes care of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.15,1:18:41.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我没事的，放心吧！\N{\rEng}I'll be alright!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.36,1:19:20.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,列哥，你跟立姐走，我不想跟你们一起去\N{\rEng}Rick, you go with Lap. I don't wanna go with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.36,1:19:23.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,你开什么玩笑？\N{\rEng}Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.73,1:19:25.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我说真的\N{\rEng}No, I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.46,1:19:28.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿立，他怎么了？\N{\rEng}Lap, what's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.69,1:19:32.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了，我不喜欢菲律宾\N{\rEng}Philippines isn't my ideal place.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.76,1:19:34.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且这件事与我无关\N{\rEng}And it's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.66,1:19:37.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我没必要走，我喜欢香港\N{\rEng}I love Hong Kong so I don't have to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.16,1:19:44.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，有话直说，不要放在心里\N{\rEng}Cheung, just say what you wanna say.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.80,1:19:52.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果当我是朋友，说出来大伙儿一起解决吧\N{\rEng}If you treat me as friend, just say it. We solve the problem together.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.63,1:19:59.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,有些事根本不能解决\N{\rEng}Some problems can't be solved.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.77,1:20:06.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 阿列  - 立姐\N{\rEng}- Rick  - Lap
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.53,1:20:08.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.50,1:20:11.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,有些事不知道比知道好\N{\rEng}You'd better ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.50,1:20:13.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,说出来大家都没意思\N{\rEng}It's no use to talk out.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.27,1:20:17.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,总之你不走，全都不要走\N{\rEng}If you don't go, all of us will stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.50,1:20:18.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿列\N{\rEng}Rick
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.70,1:20:22.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,说！\N{\rEng}Say it!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.24,1:20:28.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥他…\N{\rEng}Chueng...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.64,1:21:18.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥\N{\rEng}Cheung
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.35,1:21:20.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,放了我外婆！\N{\rEng}Let my grandma go.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.78,1:21:23.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎么这么没规矩？\N{\rEng}How come you are so bold?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.51,1:21:25.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样跟我说话\N{\rEng}How dare you talk to me in this way?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.65,1:21:28.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我还有事，外婆你先回去吧\N{\rEng}I have to do other stuff. You go back first.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.45,1:21:34.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,送外婆回去\N{\rEng}Accompany her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.68,1:21:40.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，你们老板人真好\N{\rEng}Cheung, you boss is such a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.05,1:21:44.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,还请我吃西瓜，你可要好好做事\N{\rEng}He even treated me watermelon. You should work hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.45,1:21:57.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,一个人？\N{\rEng}Alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.28,1:21:59.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,就你一个人回来？\N{\rEng}You come back alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.79,1:22:02.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,何必为一个女人弄得这么严重？\N{\rEng}Why do you have to make trouble because of a woman?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.52,1:22:07.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,好样的，出一出去就充老大\N{\rEng}That's awesome. You become the leader now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.05,1:22:09.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,教训我？\N{\rEng}Give me a lesson?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.42,1:22:12.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，立姐已经不在香港了\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen, Lap has left Hong Kong already.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.29,1:22:15.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,上哪儿去了？\N{\rEng}Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.16,1:22:41.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,说！\N{\rEng}Say it!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.26,1:22:44.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,不知道，我真的不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know. I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.13,1:22:53.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道他一定不会放过阿祥\N{\rEng}I know he won't let Cheung go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.03,1:22:55.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不应该丢下他\N{\rEng}We shouldn't leave him behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.56,1:22:57.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,可我又那么想跟你一起走\N{\rEng}But I do want to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.39,1:22:59.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,等了那么多年才等到今天\N{\rEng}For the coming of this day, I have been waiting for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.06,1:23:02.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么会弄成这样？\N{\rEng}How come it result in this way?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.00,1:23:04.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,本来就与他无关\N{\rEng}It's none of his business
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.46,1:23:08.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,跟你去菲律宾那次一样\N{\rEng}just like that time you went to Philippines.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.93,1:23:11.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,这种事怎么又发生呢？\N{\rEng}How come it happen again?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.56,1:23:16.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我害了他，是我害了他\N{\rEng}It's my fault. I get him involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.64,1:23:48.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们俩回去\N{\rEng}We go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.74,1:23:58.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,神爷，电话，是大小姐\N{\rEng}Godfather Shen, phone call from Miss Lap.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.00,1:26:16.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,阿祥，快过来\N{\rEng}Cheung, come here quickly.
